description: Calissio Resources Group, Inc. undertakes the exploration and production of copper resource on its Jovita mining property. It acquires and develops base metals projects in Mexico. The company was formerly known as Amarium Technologies, Inc. and changed its name to Calissio Resources Group, Inc. in October 2014. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada. As of September 10, 2015, Calissio Resources Group, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Industrias Calissio Sur Sa.
